When creating new rules follow these rules:

- Use the structure of rules like [react-compiler-extra.ts](mdc:src/react-compiler-extra.ts)
- Add the rule to [rules.ts](mdc:src/rules/rules.ts) index
- Start by writing tests for the rule, only then write the rule implementation
